WEBVTT

00:00:15.390 --> 00:00:17.059
[TWILIGHT]
My target is a threat to peace

00:00:17.100 --> 00:00:20.395
between East and West:
Donovan Desmond.

00:00:20.437 --> 00:00:21.605
To infiltrate his circle,

00:00:21.647 --> 00:00:24.650
the first step was to enroll
Anya in Eden College,

00:00:24.691 --> 00:00:27.194
the exclusive school
his son attends.

00:00:27.236 --> 00:00:29.154
The next step is to
secure an invitation

00:00:29.196 --> 00:00:31.782
to his social gatherings,
and to do that,

00:00:31.823 --> 00:00:35.327
Anya must acquire eight
merits, or Stella.

00:00:35.369 --> 00:00:39.831
Once those are collected, she'll
become an Imperial Scholar.

00:00:41.708 --> 00:00:43.043
[TWILIGHT]
However, at Eden,

00:00:43.085 --> 00:00:46.296
that accomplishment will
prove very difficult.

00:00:46.338 --> 00:00:50.425
So I devised plan B:
The Friendship Scheme.

00:00:50.467 --> 00:00:52.302
That plan hinges on
Anya getting closer

00:00:52.344 --> 00:00:54.972
to Desmond's son, Damian.

00:00:55.013 --> 00:00:55.556
Which in turn,

00:00:55.597 --> 00:00:59.434
should prove to connect
the target and I as parents.

00:00:59.476 --> 00:01:02.312
But on the very first day,
she punched him.

00:01:02.354 --> 00:01:06.233
Now she has a Tonitrus Bolt
and possible enemy.

00:01:09.152 --> 00:01:12.364
[TWILIGHT]
Well, the mission must proceed.

00:01:12.406 --> 00:01:14.616
We're only getting started.

00:02:51.672 --> 00:02:53.048
Good morning, Loid.

00:02:53.090 --> 00:02:56.385
[TWILIGHT] Morning, Yor.
Breakfast is ready.

00:02:56.426 --> 00:03:00.097
[TWILIGHT] Seems the three of us
are getting used to family life.

00:03:00.138 --> 00:03:03.558
Guess Anya must still
be in bed, huh? Hm?

00:03:07.229 --> 00:03:10.148
[TWILIGHT] She's embarrassed
about the fight.

00:03:10.190 --> 00:03:12.109
Come on, Anya. I'm not mad.

00:03:12.150 --> 00:03:14.403
Now hurry, so you won't be late.

00:03:17.823 --> 00:03:20.867
I'm really sorry I'm
already so bad at school.

00:03:20.909 --> 00:03:23.328
Actually, I think
that was my fault.

00:03:23.370 --> 00:03:25.288
We can't go back and change it.

00:03:25.330 --> 00:03:28.917
Just be good and try not
to get into more fights.

00:03:28.959 --> 00:03:33.213
All right? So cheer up.
Your classes start today.

00:03:33.255 --> 00:03:36.717
That's sweet, Loid.
How understanding.

00:03:36.758 --> 00:03:38.427
[TWILIGHT] Focusing on
our next move forward

00:03:38.468 --> 00:03:42.347
is far more constructive than
dwelling on past mistakes.

00:03:42.389 --> 00:03:44.891
Not to mention, we need to
keep her attitude positive

00:03:44.933 --> 00:03:48.103
about school so she
still wants to go.

00:03:48.145 --> 00:03:49.813
Meaning that for the
sake of this mission,

00:03:49.855 --> 00:03:54.276
her school life needs to go
as smoothly as possible.

00:03:54.317 --> 00:03:56.528
Oh, please make
sure you apologize

00:03:56.570 --> 00:03:58.113
to Damian at school today.

00:03:58.155 --> 00:03:58.947
Okay, Anya?

00:03:58.989 --> 00:04:02.075
Yeah. Gonna go now.

00:04:04.995 --> 00:04:07.539
Do your best like a good girl!

00:04:07.581 --> 00:04:09.750
I guess it's time for
us to go to work, too.

00:04:09.791 --> 00:04:11.960
[TWILIGHT]
Mm-hm.

00:04:12.002 --> 00:04:15.422
[TWILIGHT]
I'm counting on you, Anya.

00:04:15.464 --> 00:04:19.342
World peace rests on
you two making amends.

00:04:21.261 --> 00:04:23.513
Gonna do my best.

