[bell rings]

00:08:00.021 --> 00:08:01.690
[MATH INSTRUCTOR A] She fell
asleep in the first class

00:08:01.731 --> 00:08:02.983
on the first day?

00:08:03.024 --> 00:08:05.026
And she hit someone?
She's trouble.

00:08:05.068 --> 00:08:08.822
[BECKY] Anya! We have science
class next. Wake up!

00:08:10.073 --> 00:08:12.993
[ANYA] Second son! Gotta say
sorry to the second son.

00:08:13.034 --> 00:08:16.371
To who? To Damian?
That jerk left already.

00:08:16.413 --> 00:08:18.498
I'd just leave him alone, Anya.

00:08:18.540 --> 00:08:20.250
[ANYA] But we gotta
make up for world peace!

00:08:20.291 --> 00:08:21.835
