world, don't you?

00:08:27.090 --> 00:08:28.341
I suppose there's no telling

00:08:28.383 --> 00:08:31.177
what a boy like
that will try to do.

00:08:32.846 --> 00:08:34.139
Don't worry, Anya.

00:08:34.180 --> 00:08:36.850
Because you've got me
on your side all the way!

00:08:36.891 --> 00:08:41.062
And no matter what,
I'm gonna help protect you!

00:08:41.104 --> 00:08:42.397
[ANYA]
Oh, it's okay, then.

00:08:42.439 --> 00:08:42.981
[BECKY]
Yes.

00:08:43.023 --> 00:08:45.108
[TWILIGHT]
No, it's not!

00:08:45.150 --> 00:08:46.860
[ANYA]
Uh! Papa?

00:08:46.901 --> 00:08:48.987
[TWILIGHT] I need to find a way
to tell her how important

00:08:49.029 --> 00:08:50.905
