[TWILIGHT] Apologize, Anya.
Patch things up with him.

00:09:12.260 --> 00:09:15.722
[ANYA] I'm feeling a lot of
pressure all of a sudden.

00:09:15.764 --> 00:09:18.808
[STUDENT F] "And that's when
